      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="name_folder" data-step-uuid="A482B439-D09A-4B28-BDC5-C848933FB13C">
    <h2 id="name_folder" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Name Folder</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/330/841/original/2a82736e-668a-47d8-9f65-d513a00ab423.png" srcset="" alt="Name Folder" height="149" width="773">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_AA77A170-2156-0135-CCCA-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Type the name of the folder in<strong> Name</strong> field [1]. To save the name of the file, press Return (Mac) or Enter (PC) key or click the <strong>Check</strong> button [2]. To return to the previous title, click the <strong>Cancel</strong> button [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

